Preheat oven to 325 degrees F. Wash and sort cranberries. Combine sugar, orange marmalade, vinegar, port, raisins, curry powder, pumpkin pie spice and salt in a large bowl. Add cranberries and mix well. Spray a 2-quart baking dish with cooking spray. Pour in cranberries and cover with foil. Bake for 1 hour until cranberries are soft.